fields.name: Dark past
fields.detail: "Dark Past" is a hauntingly alluring brew that beckons you into the shadows of flavor. This enigmatic beer whispers secrets of roasted malt, its depths shrouded in the mysteries of chocolate and coffee notes. As you raise your glass to your lips, you'll feel an ancient, smoky embrace that transports you to a time when the night held secrets untold. Sip slowly, and let the intricate blend of malts and a touch of dark magic guide you through the enigmatic depths of "Dark Past," where every swallow unveils a new layer of darkness..

fields.name: Shadowbane Stout
fields.detail: Description: This obsidian elixir is brewed under the veil of the new moon, imparting a taste as dark as a sorcerer's heart. It possesses an otherworldly bitterness that beckons the shadows to dance upon your tongue.

fields.name: Witching Hour Wraith Ale
fields.detail: Description: The Witching Hour Wraith Ale is a sinister potion that captures the essence of midnight rituals. Each sip is a journey into the abyss, a harmonious blend of roasted malts and the ghostly presence of blackberries.

fields.name: Cursed Cauldron Dark Porter
fields.detail: Description: Brewed in the cursed cauldrons of the underworld, this porter is as black as the depths of despair. With notes of charred oak and arcane spices, it awakens the darkest recesses of your soul.

fields.name: Necromancer's Obscura
fields.detail: Description: The Necromancer's Obscura is an enigmatic brew that whispers of forbidden knowledge. Its flavor is a fusion of forbidden fruits and burnt offerings, leaving an eerie warmth in its wake.

fields.name: Abyssal Sorcery Stout
fields.detail: Description: This eldritch potion is steeped in the deepest abyss of forbidden sorcery. With a pitch-black body and hints of licorice and black currant, it promises to unlock your inner darkness.

fields.name: Warlock's Ebon Elixir
fields.detail: Description: Crafted by warlocks during the lunar eclipse, this elixir enchants the senses with flavors of dark chocolate and blood oranges. Its essence captures the malevolent spirit of the arcane.

fields.name: Shadowcaster's Sinister Saison
fields.detail: Description: The Shadowcaster's Sinister Saison is a wicked brew that dances between realms. It boasts a haunting blend of spices and herbs, revealing secrets as ancient as the darkest shadows.

fields.name: Nightshade Alchemist Dark Ale
fields.detail: Description: A potion straight from the alchemist's secret vault, Nightshade Ale combines the essence of night-blooming flowers with a touch of forbidden herbs. It's a potion for those who dare to embrace the forbidden.

fields.name: Dark Enchanter's Draught
fields.detail: Description: The Dark Enchanter's Draught is a bewitched brew that holds the power of forgotten enchantments. It possesses the essence of wild berries, cloaked in the mysteries of an enchanted forest.

fields.name: Wicked Warlord's Wheatwine
fields.detail: Description: The Wicked Warlord's Wheatwine is a treacherous elixir, aged in the darkest dungeons. With flavors of spiced honey and molasses, it lures you into a web of beguiling enchantment.

fields.name: Bloodmoon Witch's Bane
fields.detail: Description: The Bloodmoon Witch's Bane is a potion of perilous allure, brewed under the crimson moon. It carries the essence of forbidden orchids and blood oranges, a temptation for the senses.

fields.name: Cursed Chalice Chardonnay
fields.detail: Description: This cursed chalice of Chardonnay is an enchanting elixir that beckons from the abyss. Its flavors are as haunting as a ghost's kiss, with notes of ghost apples and charred oak.

fields.name: Nightshade Nocturne Lager
fields.detail: Description: The Nightshade Nocturne Lager is a chilling libation, capturing the essence of moonlit poison. It blends dark malts with hints of nightshade, leaving a haunting imprint on your soul.

fields.name: Enigmatic Eremite's Stout
fields.detail: Description: Brewed by reclusive hermits who dabble in the forbidden arts, this stout offers a journey into the unknown. Notes of elderberries and arcane herbs unfold like a dark incantation.

fields.name: Haunted Hollows Hefeweizen
fields.detail: Description: Haunted Hollows Hefeweizen is a mysterious elixir from the heart of spectral woods. Its flavors invoke visions of forgotten rituals, with hints of clove, banana, and spectral whispers.

fields.name: Phantom’s Ebon Ember Ale
fields.detail: Description: This sinister brew is a testament to the spectral fire that burns within. With dark roasted coffee notes and the smokiness of a witch's cauldron, it's a toast to the spirits of the beyond.

fields.name: Midnight Mage's Mead
fields.detail: Description: The Midnight Mage's Mead is a potion fit for wizards of the darkest hour. Infused with the essence of enchanted honey and blackberries, it promises a journey to the shadow realms.

fields.name: Wraithcaller's Whispering Wheat
fields.detail: Description: A wheat beer that beckons the spirits from the netherworld, the Wraithcaller's Whispering Wheat carries the haunting flavors of ghostly wheat fields and ethereal whispers.

fields.name: Forbidden Enchantress ESB
fields.detail: Description: The Forbidden Enchantress ESB is a bewitched brew, resonating with the energy of ancient enchantresses. Its flavor, a fusion of enchanted toffee and forbidden fruit, is an invitation to darkness.

fields.name: Blackheart Sorcerer's Saison
fields.detail: Description: The Blackheart Sorcerer's Saison is a brew that captures the essence of black magic. With mystical spices and the allure of black plums, it holds a charm that resonates with the depths of the soul.

fields.name: Dead-souls elixir
fields.detail: Only a being with a truly dark soul can drink this elixir. If there is even a little light in the soul, after drinking this you will plunge into the shadow realm.

fields.name: Chivalrous Elixir
fields.detail: Description: Crafted by noble knights, this golden brew is a testament to chivalry and courage. Its flavors blend the sweetness of honey and the essence of wildflowers, capturing the spirit of a knight's unwavering love for his lady.

fields.name: Lady's Grace Golden Ale
fields.detail: Description: The Lady's Grace Golden Ale is a radiant elixir that pays homage to the virtues of a knight's heart. It is imbued with the enchanting flavors of sun-kissed peaches and a touch of celestial magic.

fields.name: Paladin's Valor Pilsner
fields.detail: Description: A brew fit for paladins and champions, this Pilsner embodies the essence of valor and light magic. With notes of crisp citrus and the purity of mountain springs, it's a tribute to noble knights.

fields.name: Radiant Lance Lager
fields.detail: Description: The Radiant Lance Lager is a radiant elixir that shimmers with the light of a knight's unwavering devotion. Its flavor profile is a harmonious blend of golden grains and the delicate aroma of jasmine.

fields.name: Luminous Lady's Saison
fields.detail: Description: Brewed in honor of the radiant ladies who inspire knights, this Saison is a symbol of love and courage. It boasts a bouquet of rose petals and the refreshing essence of meadows.

fields.name: Knight's Enchantment ESB
fields.detail: Description: A beer that enchants the soul like a knight under a fair lady's spell, the Knight's Enchantment ESB combines the warmth of caramel malt with the grace of lavender blossoms.

fields.name: Sir Galahad's Golden Grail
fields.detail: Sir Galahad's Golden Grail is a beer that echoes the quest for noble purity. With flavors of golden wheat and celestial nectar, it's a tribute to the knight's relentless pursuit of a virtuous lady's heart.

fields.name: Valor's Heart Wheatwine
fields.detail: The Valor's Heart Wheatwine is a testament to a knight's inner strength and his deep love for a lady. With flavors of candied apricot and the embrace of sun-ripened grains, it's a treasure of the heart.

fields.name: Chalice of Devotion Dunkel
fields.detail: Description: The Chalice of Devotion Dunkel is a brew of unwavering loyalty and love. It combines the rich embrace of chocolate malt with a hint of enchanting vanilla, reminiscent of a knight's devotion to his lady fair.

fields.name: Graceful Guardian Golden Stout
fields.detail: Description: This golden stout is a tribute to the grace and guardianship of knights. It holds flavors of hazelnut and the gentle warmth of moonlit courtyards, embodying a knight's enduring affection for his lady.

fields.name: Lancelot's Radiant Reserve
fields.detail: Description: Lancelot's Radiant Reserve is a magical elixir that captures the light of a knight's devotion. With hints of sun-drenched plums and a touch of celestial honey, it's a symbol of unyielding love.

fields.name: Lady's Laurel Ale
fields.detail: Description: The Lady's Laurel Ale is a brew that reflects the honor bestowed upon knights. It offers the flavors of sweet laurel leaves and a whisper of meadow blossoms, symbolizing the love of a knight for his lady.

fields.name: Gallant Grail Gose
fields.detail: The Gallant Grail Gose is a mystical potion that invokes a knight's quest for his lady's favor. It combines the essence of sea salt and the purity of spring blossoms, leaving a taste of devotion on the tongue.

fields.name: Enchanted Embrace Elixir
fields.detail: Description: An elixir that embodies the enchanting embrace of knights and their beloved ladies, it carries flavors of caramelized figs and the essence of moonlit gardens, weaving tales of love and valor

fields.name: Celestial Courtship Cream Ale
fields.detail: Description: The Celestial Courtship Cream Ale is a radiant brew that symbolizes the celestial bond between a knight and his lady. Its flavors marry the sweetness of cream with the delicate notes of stardust.

fields.name: Love's Luster Lager
fields.detail: Love's Luster Lager is a golden elixir that glistens with the brilliance of chivalry. Its flavors are a harmonious blend of sun-kissed grains and the gentle caress of a lady's affection.

fields.name: Noble Knight's Nectar
fields.detail: Description: A nectar fit for noble knights, this elixir embodies the essence of valor and light. With notes of golden apples and the sweetness of honeysuckle, it's a tribute to chivalry's luminous spirit.

fields.name: Radiant Rosemary Reserve
fields.detail: Description: The Radiant Rosemary Reserve is a brew inspired by a knight's love for his lady. It blends the enchanting flavors of rosemary and the gentle kiss of spring blossoms, embodying the essence of courtly love.

fields.name: Lady's Knightlight Kölsch
fields.detail: The Lady's Knightlight Kölsch is a radiant brew that captures the essence of a knight's unwavering loyalty. It offers the flavors of crisp pears and the delicate touch of a lady's grace.

fields.name: Moonlit Serenade Saison
fields.detail: The Moonlit Serenade Saison is a brew of ethereal romance, inspired by moonlit courtyards and knightly serenades. With notes of lavender and the enchantment of starlight, it evokes the inner courage and love of a knight for his lady.
